    <p>Dear {!IF(relatedTo.Receipt_Assigned_To__c == 'Account',relatedTo.Account__r.Name,relatedTo.Contact__r.FirstName)},</p>
    <p>Thank you for your contribution of&nbsp;<apex:outputText value="${0, number,#,##0.00}">
<apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Amount__c}" />
</apex:outputText> to LiveDifferent. Your generosity helps us make a positive impact and we are deeply grateful for your compassion and commitment.</p>

<p>Your support is instrumental in helping us build hope and create lasting change in our global community. With your help, we can continue to inspire others to LiveDifferent—please visit <a href='https://LiveDifferent.com'>LiveDifferent.com</a> to learn more about our programs and how you can continue to make a meaningful impact.</p> 

<p>Once again, thank you so much for your kindness and for believing in us!</p> 

<p><br />
<br />
